description:
Wakamatsu Miyuki is one of the two main female characters in the series. Younger sister of Wakamatsu Masato, although not related by blood. Has been studying in the States for the last 6 years and has only just recently returned to Japan. An extremely cute, smart and talented girl, with lots of admirers. Acts very caring towards her older brother.
Source: AdachiFan
name: Wakamatsu Miyuki
